trans-unit.source: Represents a runtime handle for a module.
trans-unit.target: 모듈에 대 한 런타임 핸들을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveFieldHandle%2A>, <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveMethodHandle%2A>, and <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveTypeHandle%2A> methods provide efficient resolution of metadata tokens to runtime handles for fields, methods, and types in the current module.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveFieldHandle%2A>, <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveMethodHandle%2A>, 및 <xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveTypeHandle%2A>메서드 필드, 메서드 및 현재 모듈의 형식에 런타임 핸들에 메타 데이터 토큰의 효율적인 확인을 제공 합니다.</xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveTypeHandle%2A> </xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveMethodHandle%2A> </xref:System.ModuleHandle.ResolveFieldHandle%2A>
